OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBT strike: Thousands of    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers to take action for 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftwo days                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 40,000 workers at telecoms   
OL,6, giant BT are to take part in two       
OL,7, 24-hour strikes in a row over pay,     
OL,8, their union has announced.             
OL,10,FThe Communication Workers Union (CWU), 
OL,11,Fwhich represents the employees at BT,  
OL,12,Fsaid that company bosses had "stuck two
OL,13,Ffingers up" to key workers.            
OL,15,FThe strikes will take place on 29 July 
OL,16,Fand 1 August.                          
OL,18,FBT said it had made its best pay offer 
OL,19,Fand would not be re-opening the 2022   
OL,20,Fpay review.                            
